\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Exact ice-manifold thermodynamics (per spin) from the projected effective Hamiltonian. (a) Specific heat of the $32$-site FCC cluster at $J_{\pm }=-0.05\,J_{zz}$: the bare cluster peaks at the artifact scale $g_{4}$; the clean ($\bm  {\delta }=0$) cluster peaks at the photon scale $g_{\mathrm  {hex}}$. (b) $T_{\rm  peak}/g_{\mathrm  {hex}}$ vs.\ coupling for both clusters: the bare peak drifts as $J_{zz}/3|J_{\pm }|$ (dotted), the finite-size signature of the winding four-loop, while the clean peak is flat and $O(1)$ in units of $g_{\mathrm  {hex}}$. (c) Entropy: both curves release the full ice entropy $\ln (\#\mathrm  {ice})/N$ at high $T$, but the clean cluster releases the low-$T$ photon entropy at the physical scale.}}{2}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:results}{{2}{2}{Exact ice-manifold thermodynamics (per spin) from the projected effective Hamiltonian. (a) Specific heat of the $32$-site FCC cluster at $\Jpm =-0.05\,\Jzz $: the bare cluster peaks at the artifact scale $\gfour $; the clean ($\bdelta =0$) cluster peaks at the photon scale $\ghex $. (b) $T_{\rm peak}/\ghex $ vs.\ coupling for both clusters: the bare peak drifts as $\Jzz /3|\Jpm |$ (dotted), the finite-size signature of the winding four-loop, while the clean peak is flat and $O(1)$ in units of $\ghex $. (c) Entropy: both curves release the full ice entropy $\ln (\#\mathrm {ice})/N$ at high $T$, but the clean cluster releases the low-$T$ photon entropy at the physical scale}{figure.2}{}}
